<p><span class="anchor" id="p58"></span>من ذكر وَأُنْثَى<a href="#p58" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p59"></span>وَإِن اخْتلف دينهما<a href="#p59" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p60"></span>فَتجب على الْمُسلم نَفَقَة الْكَافِر<a href="#p60" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>